  ### **Go further**
  
  Lyria 3 and Lyria 3 Pro can be used with our other generative media models on Vertex AI.
  
  - **Lyria + Veo:** Generate video assets using Veo, and then dictate the exact structural timing in Lyria 3 Pro to score a custom soundtrack that matches every scene transition.
  
  - **Lyria + Nano Banana:** Generate images of a storyboard or vibe, and let Lyria create a song based on those images.
  
  - **Lyria + Gemini:** If you are struggling to define your desired sound, use Gemini to analyze your creative brief and output a highly descriptive prompt to feed into Lyria 3 models. Gemini can also create lyrics for you based on your creative brief.
  
  - **Lyria + Agents:** If you’re using these models with our [GenMedia MCP tools](https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/vertex-ai-creative-studio/tree/main/experiments/mcp-genmedia), you can provide domain-specific sound design knowledge via this [Agent Skill](https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/vertex-ai-creative-studio/blob/main/experiments/mcp-genmedia/skills/genmedia-audio-engineer/SKILL.md).
  
  
  To get started, access the Lyria 3 models today via the API [documentation](https://docs.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/generative-ai/docs/music/generate-music), Gen AI SDK for Python [notebook](https://github.com/GoogleCloudPlatform/generative-ai/blob/main/audio/music/getting-started/lyria3_music_generation.ipynb), and in our playground [Vertex AI Media Studio.](https://console.cloud.google.com/vertex-ai/studio/media/music)
  
