  ### Prompting with images
  
  #### Upload images to capture their musical mood. Use your own photos and images, or create new ones with Nano Banana.
  
  Who’s in the image?
  
  Do they look happy or sad? What poses are they striking? What are they wearing? Are they human, animal, or alien?
  
  What’s the location?
  
  What can you see in the background? Inner city streets, or an exotic landscape? Are there people or wildlife in the background?
  
  What’s going on?
  
  Is it a posed family portrait? A hockey match? Or one man and his dog on a wilderness adventure? Lyria will interpret the setting to set the musical mood.
  
