  * * *
  
  ### Prompting vocals and lyrics
  
  #### Define your desired vocal style in detail. Share your own lyrics, or get help from Lyria by describing a theme.
  
  Create a vocal profile
  
  Do you want a male or female singer? Do they have commanding baritone vocals, or a clear and high soprano range? Is their voice rich, gravelly, soulful, breathy? And are they singing in English – or another language?
  
  Use your own lyrics
  
  Add specific lyrics by writing **Lyrics:** before the lines you’d like to hear. If you want backing singers to echo the main vocals, add that in round brackets. Like this: “ **Lyrics:** Let’s go _(go)_”.
  
  Get lyrical help from Lyria 3
  
  If you want Lyria 3 to generate lyrics for you, it’s best to make the theme clear with your prompt. You might want “a love song”, or “a song about success”. Or perhaps you want to write a “new happy birthday song” for your best friend.
  
  ![An image of a grey music generation interface. A highly technical prompt focusing on a breathy soprano lead.](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/o1JXXYC_vQR7U_QCZk-kjRGnYWlLdBVVB2dxLLJ4o7SZYlXU9tuUrgvTOcyGs8pLKjiUB4sNWpJu88iY5GALdTUPwVG1sqZ97D6wus7u_KB5sWjJ=w1440-h1080-n-nu)![An image of a grey music generation interface. A highly technical prompt focusing on a breathy soprano lead.](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/AROD6nOdreDJZZrZ8NiNaskBKOzKByFKMaPdx5tNXNZYj4Ob74zqjXlj0SE9RMVMGW7nrs2_t3X_-gF3IsktBsCX_OB6jQj_v0Ug-dLrxA81TL0e=w1440-h1080-n-nu)
  
  ![An image of a grey music generation interface. The interface displays a prompt formatted as Lyrics: "The city lights are bleeding through the rain, / We're dancing in the memories left behind. / Running at the speed of a whispered name, / Caught in a rhythm only we can find".](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/YiYGvVZgsvoGrWhnjrnVMDJ7jovogZBY27mz8nibVylbVpLLfZ63fADbJDs67DqkzWXrO3oAnH5mZkDnypxwWNbRyWRkicZoj6PQkOekpGpQi7GG9pM=w1440-h1080-n-nu)![An image of a grey music generation interface. The interface displays a prompt formatted as Lyrics: "The city lights are bleeding through the rain, / We're dancing in the memories left behind. / Running at the speed of a whispered name, / Caught in a rhythm only we can find".](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/f80xIIBp4Yaiw06SW4iKR2ySIOrs3ip8PMVHTBpyPJ-G-c_KETJhd6fcngkAIa40H8HsxNkYOAaISmL33CTUuGRgnPmrRq5MPxKeO6vUWlT0Y6QI_A=w1440-h1080-n-nu)
  
  ![An image of a grey music generation interface. The image shows a very simple, three-word input: "A love song".](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LZW4wmH1L51phbdUkTeH4U_W6pUVleDCKvN-xgwvvm2astr08y6tITXPVZxNnqx3SAnvX-WmAp9GuWBrYpUXJVLZqaT5T447pNcCbTDoEvz0N6KufA=w1440-h1080-n-nu)![An image of a grey music generation interface. The image shows a very simple, three-word input: "A love song".](https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/LnFb67cw687zin9rg7iyEcsMGBROIm59y9CVCromamIV2fbZ6-6Mi5JRuMWVmzO1GivobKy68YZqykuQJ6tV1pnXh8aI2HywjiOOEOzL1f7mbP1LUQ=w1440-h1080-n-nu)
  
